parsed.explanation: Four instances of corrupted UTF-8 sequences were fixed, specifically replacing 'B\u221a\u00bacher' with 'Bücher', 'Prei\u221a\u00fc' with 'Preiß', and correcting the format abbreviations '4t\u221a\u2264' and '8v\u221a\u2264' to '4tô' and '8vô' respectively. A crucial structural correction was made by inserting the closing tag '</BIBL>' after the Mohemii entry (<FORMAT>4tô</FORMAT>.) to prevent the subsequent book listing (Titus Livius) from being improperly nested.
